snippet: The police said Wednesday that DNA samples from the bodies of two British tourists found bludgeoned on a resort island did not match any collected from 12 people who had been in the area.
lead_paragraph: The police said Wednesday that DNA samples from the bodies of two British tourists found bludgeoned on a resort island did not match any collected from 12 people who had been in the area.

headline.main: Thailand: No DNA Matches Found in Tourists’ Killings
